--- Astroblast / Rippersnapper ---

Astroblast frowns, and replies to Stratus, "Hmm, we'll need to have 
the Terrorcons move the ship. I'll get them to transform, then I'll 
send them down to where you are. Have them bring the ship to the 
surface, and push it onto the beach. Abominus should be able to 
do that, the ship isn't that big. (the G1 Pred ship was only a 
medium or slightly smaller crusier.)

Turning to the Terrorcons, he shouts out orders, "Terrorcons, form 
Abominus."

Rippersnapper grumbles, and growls, then leaps into the air 
forming his part of Abominus.

ooC: Gotta go, making the last part of this post short. =)
